  "subject": "Improve SDC UI performance with compression and caching",
  "commit_message": "Improve SDC UI performance with compression and caching\n\n- Add gzip compression for proxied API responses via Jetty GzipFilter\n- Add Cache-Control headers for static assets (new CacheControlFilter)\n- Remove broken dcae-bundle.js reference from index.html\n- Add ETag support to /setup/ui and /dataTypes endpoints for 304 responses\n\nIssue-ID: SDC-4827\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>\nChange-Id: Ia799f7db9a923d1545f17bbcf7d239c1e6d11d05\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
